info.name: Hyperledger Besu JSON-RPC API
info.description:
Hyperledger Besu JSON-RPC API enables interaction with a Besu Ethereum node

## Notice
This is a public end-point! It is not encrypted. Encrypted RPC access involves registration!

https://github.com/freight-trust
